          "script": "// Left Paddle — Player 1 (W/S keys)\nconst SPEED = 400;\nconst HALF_H = 300;\nconst PADDLE_H = 40;\n\nif (Input.isKeyPressed(\"w\") || Input.isKeyPressed(\"W\")) {\n  self.y -= SPEED * dt;\n}\nif (Input.isKeyPressed(\"s\") || Input.isKeyPressed(\"S\")) {\n  self.y += SPEED * dt;\n}\n\n// Clamp to screen\nself.y = Math.max(-HALF_H + PADDLE_H, Math.min(HALF_H - PADDLE_H, self.y));\n"
